Interface ExperimentalParticipantPoolEnricher

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface ExperimentalParticipantPoolEnricher
extends ParticipantEvidenceEnricher<ExperimentalParticipantPool>, ParticipantPoolEnricher<ExperimentalParticipantPool,FeatureEvidence>
